          {
            "text": "A short energy statement from Day 32 of the MONEY program. The release names the habit of planning only familiar income routes; the allow opens room for income to arrive outside the plan.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
